                    <li id="responsive">Moreover, we share a long term relationship with all our <a href="clients" title="Almeka's Clients">clients</a> that goes beyond our primary projects.</li>
                </ul>

                <p>Over the past one year, responsive design commonly known as device friendly design has become quite the hot topic in the <a href="web-designing" title="Web Designing" itemprop="serviceType">web design</a> community. Under <a href="http://www.almeka.net/website-designing/" title="Responsive Website Designing" target="_blank" itemprop="serviceType">responsive design</a> or device friendly design, your website will be compatible and work perfectly well in all devices</p>

                <h3><a href="http://www.almeka.net/website-designing/" title="Responsive Website Designing" target="_blank" itemprop="serviceType">Responsive Web Designing &amp; Web Development</a>.</h3>

                <p>In the current scenario, what every one needs is  mobile version &amp; tab version of websites. UAE having the largest number of smartphone users in the world, the relevance of Responsive &amp; <a href="#retina-ready" itemprop="produces">retina ready websites</a> is huge.  In short, a single website structure has to be feasible for all these  machines and gadgets rather than create different ones for Blackberry, Apple, iPad, Netbook and lot more devices in the making. It is really impractical to create separate designs for different devices and why should we lose visitors to our site for not being available on their concerned devices? This is the kind of challenge faced by 'n' number of companies, in UAE which <a href="http://www.almeka.net/" title="Almeka Advertising &amp; Marketing" itemprop="provider">Almeka</a> has taken up and has now given a solution - <a href="http://www.almeka.net/website-designing/" title="Responsive Website Designing" target="_blank" itemprop="serviceType">Responsive web design</a>. Nowadays, in the field of web design and <a href="web-development" title="Web Development" itemprop="serviceType">web development</a>, endless new devices and resolutions are on its way and our websites should be exceptionally good and very technical to be noticeable enough.</p>
                <figure class="inner-img-2"><img src="img/Responsive_Web_Designing_and_development.jpg" alt="Responsive web designing And web development"></figure>

                <h3>What exactly is <a href="http://www.almeka.net/website-designing/" title="Responsive Website Designing" target="_blank" itemprop="serviceType">responsive web designing</a>?</h3>

                <p><a href="http://www.almeka.net/website-designing/" title="Responsive Website Designing" target="_blank" itemprop="serviceType">Responsive web designing</a> is the hottest approach in web designing &amp; <a href="web-development" title="Web Development" itemprop="serviceType" id="retina-ready">web development</a> which supports websites in such a way to respond properly to user behaviour appropriate to platform, screen size and direction. This approach involves a clever blending of flexible grids, layouts, images and intelligent use of CSS media queries. According to the technology used under <a href="http://www.almeka.net/website-designing/" title="Responsive Website Designing" target="_blank" itemprop="serviceType">responsive website designing</a>, the website automatically takes the  shape of the design being used and hence it is also known as fluid responsive design. The image size, resolution and the script are automatically accommodated on  the devices used and since  technology enables websites to  respond rapidly to all devices, its rightly termed <a href="http://www.almeka.net/website-designing/" title="Responsive Website Designing" target="_blank" itemprop="serviceType">responsive web design</a>. Finally, the need to design and develop websites for each new device is purged.</p>

                <h3>Why Retina Ready?</h3>

                <p>Almost all high end gadgets use high resolution displays which is the prospect of  the market. Since all the latest gadgets are using high resolution displays, retina ready displays are used by almost all up to date mobiles. When introducing a website, it should be completely be optimized for retina screens since more people will be able to enjoy the images in sharp pixels and not many will get irritated by blurred images and overall ambiguity. Here lies the prominence of retina ready website designs which makes your website appear beautiful and eye soothing  to visitors.</p>
                <figure id="HTML_5_CSS_3" class="inner-img-2"><img src="img/retina_ready_design.jpg" alt="Retina ready design"></figure>

                <h3>latest trends in web designing</h3>

                <p>The latest trends in web designing is HTML5 ,CSS3 and Flat UI design. HTML5 and CSS3 are now the most popular tools that aids in crafting a perfect website. Even though both has its own breakthrough, both these tools are used together in creating well defined pages with enough perfection.  The main advantage you get out of this are that the codes will be readable and  precise and thereby it will be ranked high. There is no need for extra plug ins to view audios and videos. Browser compatibility is also another benefit which HTML 5 and CSS 3 offers. Contact forms in websites designed with HTML5 and CSS3 are compatible with all the general browsers. Above all, while adopting this technology , our designing team enjoys full control over the colours in templates and need not use different codes for colour themes.  Flat UI or Flat Design is another major trend .  Flat design implies mainly flatness of style, and the interface is simplified by eliminating extra elements like textures, shadows, gradients and ll that creates a 3D look. This approach allows interface designs to be more updated and competent. Another advantage is that, since the design elements are minimum, websites are able to load faster and will look great on high definition screens even when resized.</p>

                <p>Our designing team is well versed with all the modern trends in web designing which you can see for yourself in our own website!!! Keeping in mind  that <a href="http://www.almeka.net/website-designing/" title="Responsive Website Designing" target="_blank" itemprop="serviceType">responsive design</a> is a necessity and flat UI designs are in trend,  we prioritize in creating highly functional and usable website with all modern elements and trendy features. All our projects are highly professional, meets all standard policies, highly trendy, adopt affluent colours, impressive layouts,  watertight designs, corporate blend, compact and highly secured. So, endless options are available in the years to come. We @ <a href="http://www.almeka.net/" title="Almeka Advertising &amp; Marketing" itemprop="provider">Almeka</a> is well set to give you endless opportunities  and websites crafted with high end technology to meet all your  needs, while we continue to get polished everyday to deliver the best to all our clients.</p>
